0. npm install --global cross-env

1. Redis installation
https://hub.docker.com/_/redis/

docker pull redis
docker run --name redis -p 6379:6379 -d redis // this should start on port 6379/tcp
docker start redis
In case you experience "Error: Redis connection to localhost:6379 failed - connect ECONNREFUSED 127.0.0.1:6379" please check the following:


